50                      How Ernie and Bert Came to Be
51
52     You all know Ernie and Bert- they're those two puppet guys that live in an
53apartment on Sesame Street.  You probably also have stayed up late at night
54breaking into a cold sweat because you couldn't figure out how they were
55related.  Most people(besides those k-k00l dooooodz who say "who cares,they're
56puppets") say Oh, they are gay lovers.  Well, maybe, but if so, why do they
57play with toys.  Fine, they are immature gay lovers.  No, because how do they
58pay the rent.  They don't work, and don't own a car.  Plus, they sleep in
59seperate beds.  They can't be roommates cuz they are just kids or demented
60adults.  Now that you are thoroughly confused, I will help you sort it out.
61     
62     First of all, Bert is Ernie's father.  That's why they sleep in seperate
63beds.  If you want, they can be gay and incestuous, but thats up to your sick
64little imagination.  Anyway, Bert's wife was red. In case you don't remember
65bert is yellow and ernie is orange.  Red and yellow make orange, hence ernie's
66color.
67     
68     Bert worked in a factory for several years before he came to sesame
69street(but why did he go to sesame street? - read on!) One day, Bert got just a
70little too close to that machine that crushes steel girders into pellets the
71size of a grain of salt.  His head was smashed, and he was brain damaged.  So
72severely that he regressed to the intelectual level of a small child-a child
73about ernie's age.
74     When Bert's wife realized that Bert had become a moron, she divorced him
75and took everything they owned (except that little brat Ernie).  Well, bert's
76lawyer found out and sued the wife for everything she had.  Unfortunately Bert
77and Ernie couldn't live alone so they were put into a community for the
78mentally unwell.  You got it- Sesame Street.  They met Oscar, a wierd hairy man
79obsessed with garbage.  Big Bird, a junkie and hallucinogen user  who always
80thought he was being followed by a brown elephant-like thing called
81Snuffalopagulopaloopulagus.  All the real people on sesame street are
82counselors for the deranged folks who live there.  Why else would they be so
83bloody nice all the time?  The real people kids are trucked in from nearby
84towns to act as a positive influence on the patients.
85     Well, thats it.  Years of research went into this, and it actually makes
86sense.     Remember, this is only a theory!!!  It has yet to be proven, but I'd
87like to see you find a flaw in it.
